title: JAN 12 2022 - REPEAT BOOSTER SHOTS SPUR EUROPEAN WARNING ON IMMUNE-SYSTEM RISKS
description:
On today’s episode of Human Events daily, Jack Posobiec discusses reports out of Europe detailing how repeat booster shots can compromise your immune system, the FBI refusing to answer under oath if Ray Epps is a Jan. 6th informant, how the U.S. justice department is forming a unit to counter domestic terrorism and all the latest on the Fauci emails and how he knew the pandemic was unlikely to be natural. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
